134
00:07:29,282 --> 00:07:32,785
Well, I can't understand
his actions at all.

135
00:07:32,869 --> 00:07:35,580
Well, yeah. That's true.
I can't either.

136
00:07:36,581 --> 00:07:37,665
I don't understand.

137
00:07:38,708 --> 00:07:42,504
When the girls were first talking
about which guy they were into,

138
00:07:42,587 --> 00:07:44,381
