153
00:08:34,514 --> 00:08:36,308
-This is bad.
-This is bad.

154
00:08:36,391 --> 00:08:39,394
It's really disgusting, actually.

155
00:08:39,477 --> 00:08:42,897
So the fact is that he told Yuriko
he didn't have feelings for Minori,

156
00:08:42,980 --> 00:08:44,274
and then tells everything to Minori.

157
00:08:44,357 --> 00:08:45,483
