158
00:08:45,567 --> 00:08:47,027
-It's very strange.
-It is strange.

159
00:08:47,110 --> 00:08:50,072
-Yeah, it's unnecessary.
-Yes, totally unnecessary thing to say.

160
00:08:50,155 --> 00:08:52,282
