he wanted all the women to think,

171
00:09:18,391 --> 00:09:20,477
"He's only thinking of me."

172
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:23,063
Yeah, when talking to Yuriko,

173
00:09:23,146 --> 00:09:26,108
