in front of everyone!

193
00:10:15,490 --> 00:10:17,367
She's not!

194
00:10:17,450 --> 00:10:20,787
We've established she only sees
Mr. Ticket as Mr. Ticket.

195
00:10:21,621 --> 00:10:23,665
So the guys
just misunderstand her actions.

196
00:10:23,748 --> 00:10:25,500
That's right.

197
00:10:25,583 --> 00:10:28,211
But since he says he's narrowed it down
to one at that moment,

198
00:10:28,295 --> 00:10:31,964
